name: FNF Garcello Test | Friday Night Funkin
name_original: FNF Garcello Test | Friday Night Funkin
description:
FNF Garcello Test is out!

I saw that many of you liked the last FNF Test I made with AGOTI, so, I moved at the next - the heaviest smoker in the building - Garcello!

Here you can play and test all the animations from Garcello including Headache, Nerves, Release, Fading, and some secret ones.

Now, I introduced a cutscene too! Can you guess how to open it? I think no.. 

Secret Garcello animations: 
  1.  Cough 
  2.  Tie
  3. Cutscene

All the secret keys can be found at play-games.com on the "FNF Garcello Test" game, in the description.

Download the original mod from here: https://gamebanana.com/mods/166531

Play the original mod online: https://www.play-games.com/game/27152/friday-night-funkin-vs-garcello.html
